== 規則變動 ==

=== 常規變動 ===
* 2016年9月，{{Le|自由媒體集團|Liberty Media}}先從[[CVC資本合夥公司|CVC資本合夥公司]]手中收購部分一級方程式賽車股權，預計在2017年賽季完成所有交易。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://mobile.abc.net.au/news/2016-09-08/formula-one-sells-for-$5.7b-to-liberty-media/7824932|title=Formula One sells for $5.7 billion to John Malone's Liberty Media|last=|first=|date=2016-09-08|work=abc.net.au|publisher=[[Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation|Australian Broadcasting Corporation]]|accessdate=2016-09-08|archive-date=2016-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160909195543/http://mobile.abc.net.au/news/2016-09-08/formula-one-sells-for-$5.7b-to-liberty-media/7824932|dead-url=no}}</ref>合約內容也提及，車隊將能採取與美國[[國家美式足球聯盟|國家美式足球聯盟]]及[[美國職業棒球大聯盟|美國職業棒球大聯盟]]相同的模式，對這項運動進行投資。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/126098/teams-will-get-chance-to-invest-in-f1|title=Liberty Media's F1 takeover: Teams will get the chance to invest|last=Parkes|first=Ian|date=2016-09-08|work=autosport.com|publisher=Haymarket Publications|accessdate=2016-09-08|archive-date=2016-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160909030427/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/126098/teams-will-get-chance-to-invest-in-f1|dead-url=yes}}</ref>商業運作模式也在2017年1月進行重組，[[伯尼·埃克萊斯頓|伯尼·埃克萊斯頓]]卸下了執掌超過40年的[[一級方程式集團|一級方程式集團]]執行長職務。<ref name=Sky10740560>{{cite web |url=http://news.sky.com/story/bernie-ecclestone-no-longer-f1-chief-executive-statement-10740560 |title=Bernie Ecclestone no longer F1 chief executive - statement |publisher=Sky News |accessdate=2017-01-23 |archive-date=2019-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190214185240/https://news.sky.com/story/bernie-ecclestone-no-longer-f1-chief-executive-statement-10740560 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* 以往在伯尼·埃克萊斯頓的管理下，發布任何在闈場內拍攝的畫面都需經過一級方程式管理公司嚴格控管，但隨著自由媒體集團的收購一級方程式賽車後，各家車隊將在[[社交媒體|社交媒體]]上獲得更大的權力。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://mobile.abc.net.au/news/2017-02-28/formula-one-relaxes-social-media-rules-for-teams/8309282?section=sport|title=Formula One relaxes social media rules under post-Bernie Ecclestone regime as testing begins|work=abc.net.au|publisher=[[Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation|Australian Broadcasting Corporation]]|date=2017-02-28|accessdate=2017-02-28|archive-date=2017-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170228031132/http://mobile.abc.net.au/news/2017-02-28/formula-one-relaxes-social-media-rules-for-teams/8309282?section=sport|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 國際汽聯要求舉辦賽事的每條賽道加強賽道的防護措施，以應對因技術規則變動而帶來近{{convert|40|kph|mph|1|abbr=off}}的彎道速度提升。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.speedcafe.com/2017/01/18/fia-requests-upgrades-f1-circuits-2017/|title=FIA requests upgrades to F1 circuits for 2017|work=speedcafe.com|date=2017-01-18|accessdate=2017-01-18|archive-date=2017-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170910185246/http://www.speedcafe.com/2017/01/18/fia-requests-upgrades-f1-circuits-2017/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

