* 賽會為了使2017年的賽車較前一季提升4至5秒的單圈速度，於是對車身設計的技術規則進行修改。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.jamesallenonf1.com/2016/03/f1-rules-elimination-qualifying-confirmed-for-australia-2017-cars-5-secs-faster/|title=F1 rules: elimination qualifying confirmed for Australia, 2017 cars "five seconds faster"|work=James Allen on F1|publisher=James Allen|accessdate=2016-03-06|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305101142/http://www.jamesallenonf1.com/2016/03/f1-rules-elimination-qualifying-confirmed-for-australia-2017-cars-5-secs-faster/|dead-url=no}}</ref>修改部分如下：<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2016/05/10/side-side-compare-f1-cars-2016-2017/|title=Side-by-side: How the 2017 rules will change F1 design|first=Will|last=Tyson|work=F1 Fanatic|publisher=Keith Collantine|date=2016-05-11|accessdate=2016-05-11|archive-date=2016-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160510175450/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2016/05/10/side-side-compare-f1-cars-2016-2017/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
** 車體總寬增加至{{convert|2000|mm|in|1|abbr=off}}。<ref name="2017changes">{{cite web|url=https://www.formula1.com/en/championship/inside-f1/rules-regs/2017-season-changes.html|title=2017 season changes|work=formula1.com|publisher=Formula One World Championship Limited|accessdate=2017-03-11|archive-date=2017-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312090818/https://www.formula1.com/en/championship/inside-f1/rules-regs/2017-season-changes.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
** 車身寬度最窄可達{{convert|1600|mm|in|1|abbr=off}}。<ref name="2017changes" />
** 前鼻翼的寬度增加至{{convert|1800|mm|in|1|abbr=off}}。
** 尾翼的高度降低{{convert|150|mm|in|1|abbr=off}}，並後移{{convert|200|mm|in|1|abbr=off}}。
** 更大且更長的擴散器，在現行的規則下，擴散器的起點可位於距離後輪中心線{{convert|175|mm|in|1|abbr=off}}的位置。<ref name="2017changes" />
** 前移{{le|破風板|bargeboard (aerodynamics)}}的前緣，提升車隊控制氣流的自由度。
** 增加前輪及後輪的寬度（較往年寬約25%），使車輛獲得更大的機械抓地力。<ref name="2017changes" />
** 車輛最低重量限制增加20公斤至722公斤，允許車隊使用105公斤的燃油以因應最低車重限制的增加。
* 廢除為動力單元研發制定的配額制度（將動力單元分為兩個區塊，每個區塊配有一定的額度，根據製造商對其研發的次數扣除其配額）。<ref name="obligation to supply">{{cite news|url=http://www.speedcafe.com/2016/04/30/fia-confirms-new-2017-engine-regulations/|title=FIA confirms new 2017 engine regulations|work=speedcafe.com|date=2016-04-30|accessdate=2016-04-30|archive-date=2017-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807153406/http://www.speedcafe.com/2016/04/30/fia-confirms-new-2017-engine-regulations/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
* 針對每個構成動力單元部件的尺寸、重量及材料加以限制。<ref name="allen 2020">{{cite news|url=http://www.jamesallenonf1.com/2016/04/analysis-important-deal-agreed-on-f1-engines-to-2020/|title=Aanalysis: Important deal agreed on F1 engines to 2020|first=James|last=Allen|work=James Allen on F1|publisher=James Allen|date=2016-04-29|accessdate=2016-04-30|archive-date=2016-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160430121359/http://www.jamesallenonf1.com/2016/04/analysis-important-deal-agreed-on-f1-engines-to-2020/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 在過往賽季的規則中，曾訂定若該賽季超過20場大獎賽，則可以使用5套{{le|一級方程式賽車引擎|Formula One engines|動力單元}}；這條規則在2017年被廢除，無論賽季共有幾場大獎賽，每支車隊皆僅能使用4套動力單元。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/124241/how-f1-new-engine-rules-will-work|title=How Formula 1's new engine rules will work|first1=Ian|last1=Parkes|first2=Lawrence|last2=Barretto|work=autosport.com|publisher=Haymarket Publications|date=2016-05-12|accessdate=2016-05-12|archive-date=2016-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160516152934/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/124241/how-f1-new-engine-rules-will-work|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
* 2017年的引擎供給費用減少100萬[[歐元|歐元]]，到了2018年將有更一步降低成本。<ref name="allen 2020"/>
* 禁止將車載攝影機裝置在前鼻錐上。<ref name="wmsc 9/30">{{cite web|url=http://www.fia.com/news/fia-announces-world-motor-sport-council-decisions|title=FIA announces World Motor Sport Council decisions|date=2015-09-30|accessdate=2015-10-02|archive-date=2015-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002134042/http://www.fia.com/news/fia-announces-world-motor-sport-council-decisions|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* [[倍耐力|倍耐力]]持續在2017年擔任一級方程式賽車獨家輪胎供應商。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Galloway|first1=James|title=Pirelli to stay as F1's sole tyre supplier until 2019 season|url=http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10025880/pirelli-to-stay-as-f1s-sole-tyre-supplier-until-2019-season|publisher=Sky Sports|accessdate=2017-03-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301141227/http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10025880/pirelli-to-stay-as-f1s-sole-tyre-supplier-until-2019-season|archivedate=2017-03-01|date=2015-10-12|deadurl=yes}}</ref>如同過往幾個賽季，該公司提供5種乾胎及2種雨胎，共7種不同的輪胎配方。每場大獎賽皆能使用2款濕地配方，在乾胎方面，每支車隊僅能選擇3種在整個比賽週末使用。<ref>{{cite web|title=F1® Tires Range|url=https://www.pirelli.com/tires/en-us/motorsport/formula-one/tire-range#|publisher=[[Pirelli|Pirelli]]|accessdate=2017-03-01|archive-date=2017-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170302025555/https://www.pirelli.com/tires/en-us/motorsport/formula-one/tire-range|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Tyres and wheels|url=https://www.formula1.com/en/championship/inside-f1/rules-regs/tyres-and-wheels.html|website=formula1.com|publisher=Formula One World Championship Limited|accessdate=2017-03-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301141640/https://www.formula1.com/en/championship/inside-f1/rules-regs/tyres-and-wheels.html|archivedate=2017-03-01|deadurl=yes}}</ref>正如前一賽季，在整個比賽週末期間使用的13套輪胎中，每支車隊能夠從倍耐力提供的此3種配方中決定剩餘的10套輪胎選擇。然而，新配方在冬季測試的時間有限，倍耐力將統一分配各隊在前5場比賽的輪胎選擇套數。<ref>{{cite web|title=Formel 1 - Neues Design, neue Regeln, schnellere Autos|url=http://www.sportschau.de/weitere/formel1/das-ist-neu-in-der-formel-eins-100.html|publisher=Sportschau|accessdate=2017-03-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301140233/http://www.sportschau.de/weitere/formel1/das-ist-neu-in-der-formel-eins-100.html|archivedate=2017-03-01|date=2017-03-01|language=de|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

